265.description: You may be eligible for the Rental Housing Allowance for Families Program if you meet the following eligibility requirements:

267.description: You are a Yukon resident. (You have lived in Yukon for at least 90 days.)

268.description: You are currently renting or looking to rent a modest private market rental home or apartment.

269.description: You have at least one dependent in the home as defined by the Canada Revenue Agency (please see definition in the

271.description: You are paying more than 30% of gross household income on total housing expenses (rent and utilities).

273.description: (If you have arrears, you must pay them in full before you will be approved for this program).
